nginx/nginx.conf:

events {}

http {
    upstream my_app {
        server app1:3000;
        server app2:3000;
    }

    server {
        listen 80;

        location / {
            proxy_pass http://my_app;
        }
    }
}


nginx/Dockerfile:

FROM nginx:alpine
COPY nginx.conf /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
EXPOSE 80


Explanation:

upstream my_app defines the backend servers.

proxy_pass sends requests to my_app.

Requests are load balanced between app1 and app2.
